  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The principal aim is to assess if a simple test, the time it takes to walk 10 meters for a
      patient about to be discharged after a hospital stay for an acute illness, is related to the
      risk of readmission.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
